reviewText: Use To Be Great! I use this app daily, I would love to see more options for keeping track of movies watched vs movies owned and movies needed for my collection.

reviewText: Beyond good. This app is truly awesome. The UI is both beautiful and functional. And the offline caching system is excellent. Now I can't manage without this app.

author: Fahim Faisal
reviewText: It works incredibly well and very intuitive to use So out of all the TV Trackers, IMO this is the best one. It looks great, the UI is very easy to use and even though it looks like a simple app, it does have a ton of customization options. And the X-Pass is great if you have multiple devices, or just appreciate the dev who single handedly made this.

author: Bhavil Jain
reviewText: Great app but requires binge watching option Hi there, it's a great app to keep track of tv shows.. But I believe a normal person, like me, doesn't really have the time on everyday basis to watch all the shows that air in a day, hence we binge watch the entire season when it's over... And I think that's something you should take into consideration... If a show is marked as binge watch.. Then it should not be listed in the recent/upcoming list.. And should give a notification when the current season is over. Add that and it will be a 5 star review :)

author: Randy Arrowood
reviewText: Best TV tracker around I've tried them all, and I ALWAYS stay with Series Guide. I've been using it for years and it always just works.

author: A Google User
reviewText: New Update Best Tv show tracker App on Android. Movie section and trakt sync are excellent bonuses. Tried some of the others but this is definitely the winner. Used it for years now.

author: Jamie
reviewText: Best movie and TV show tracker app out there! Love this app, I use it daily! Also includes the option of going to premium for a one-time payment and not monthly payments like most of the other similar apps.

author: shiran salomon
reviewText: Please fix the problem I love this app really much. Few weeks ago it stopped working good, the episodes are not updated and I really though that season was ended because I didn't get update.

author: Hamar Ferenc
reviewText: It was the best on the market until... It was my fave show tracker app on the entire playstore until an update messed it up. I can't delete shows from my collection, however deleting a movie from a collection works fine. Because I'm using it only for tv series, I hate that I can't delete a show from my collection. I press remove from collection and the show remains under the collection tab. After a fix, I will give 5 stars again. Thanks.

author: Mara Zeman
reviewText: The BEST app for tracking the shows you watch! I can't recommend this app highly enough, both its design and function are top notch! Nice, visually appealing user friendly graphic interface, with a seemingly gigantic database of shows...I easily found and added everything I searched for, and I watch A LOT of different stuff! I strongly recommend spending the extra couple of bucks to get the "pro" version of this app called SeriesGuide X. It adds several incredibly useful features including additional widgets and upcoming show notifications.

author: Keepie Uppie
reviewText: Fantastic! Paid for the full version as I am that impressed. The app is very refined. Found every show I've searched for. They can be added to favourites so they appear at the top (very handy for the current shows you're watching). There's synopsis and a screenshot for each episode. Looks great (material design). One of my favourite apps.

reviewText: Good but Add more laguages TV like HINDI

reviewText: If there is archive... I would like to move finished series into archive folder and wouldn't want to see in shows list. That confuses me alot, other than that it's useful and worthy for paying.

author: Mark Mercer
reviewText: Was my one of my fav's, widget not longer updates for days after marshmallow. Not hooked to trax or any of that, I just put enter my favorite shows and look at the widget to see what is playing that evening, Widget must be forced to update, installed, did not help, rebooted more than once, does not fix the issue, wrote to the author, never heard back. Paid for it, was five stars in my books till a few months ago.

author: Gabrielle Person
reviewText: Great for keeping track of shows I watch shows on Netflix and Hulu and am catching up on some series that started years ago. Some have already ended but I need to catch up. This helps me keep track of which episodes I've seen and which I haven't.

It sucks that when I start "following" a slow on my tablet, it doesn't get tracked by my phone. I've of course linked both to my Trackt account!

Marvels Daredevil and Jessica Jones have correct times and dates on TVDB but are not showing correct on the app. Again, Orange is the New Black s01e01 shows air date as July 12th 2013 rather than July 11th
